
Run the following command:
for file in *merged.txt; do ../make_kmer_plot_query.R $file; done

This command will generate image files (png format) for all *merged.txt in the directory.
Structural variants (SVs) will be shown in image files.

*merged.txt contains the coordinates of k-mers involving SVs for two assemblies; 
(1) reference assembly (GRCh38 in this example) or baseline assembly
(2) assembly of your interst

Here are first several lines of sv.HG00438.maternal.ins.merged.txt
